title: Grateful Dead Live at Red Rocks Amphitheatre on 1978-07-08
description:
Set One	
Bertha > Good Lovin' ; Dire Wolf ; El Paso; It Must Have Been The Roses ; New Minglewood Blues ; Ramble On Rose ; The Promised Land ; Deal

Set Two	
Samson And Delilah ; Ship Of Fools ; Estimated Prophet > The Other One > Eyes Of The World > Drums > Space > Wharf Rat > Franklin's Tower > Sugar Magnoli

Encore 	
Terrapin Station > One More Saturday Night ; Werewolves Of London
